ular throughout Christendom, in part because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir Thomas Bodley was born in 1438, in Crediton, Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, Thomas Bodley, was 20 and his mother, Johanna Joan Legh, was 21. He had at least 2 sons with Lady Anna Agnus Whitebread. He died in 1473, in London, Madison, Ohio, United States, at the age of 35."},"et":{"1438–1473":"1438–1473","1438–Female":"1438–Surnud","1460–1492":"1460–1492","1465–1491":"1465–1491","1418–1438":"1418–1438","1418–Female":"1418–Surnud","Abt 1460":"umbes 1460","Abt 1465":"umbes 1465","1465":"1465","1473":"1473","1460":"1460","1492":"1492","1491":"1491","1418":"1418","1438":"1438","London, London, England":"London, Madison, Ohio, Ameerika Ühendriigid","<Of, Dunscombe, Devonshire, England>":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dunscombe, Crediton, Devon, England":"Crediton, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dunscombe, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1438–1473":"1438–1473","1438–Female":"1438–Kuollut","1460–1492":"1460–1492","1465–1491":"1465–1491","1418–1438":"1418–1438","1418–Female":"1418–Kuollut","Abt 1460":"noin 1460","Abt 1465":"noin 1465","1465":"1465","1473":"1473","1460":"1460","1492":"1492","1491":"1491","1418":"1418","1438":"1438","London, London, England":"London, Madison, Ohio, Yhdysvallat","<Of, Dunscombe, Devonshire, England>":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dunscombe, Crediton, Devon, England":"Crediton, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dunscombe, Devonshire, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1438–1473":"1438–1473","1438–Female":"1438–Décédée","1460–1492":"1460–1492","1465–1491":"1465–1491","1418–1438":"1418–1438","1418–Female":"1418–Décédée","Abt 1460":"environ 1460","Abt 1465":"environ 1465","1465":"1465","1473":"1473","1460":"1460","1